oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (split fountain, red to purple, on yellow) announcing the 6th Annual Academy of Country Music Honors celebrating ACM special award winners including Bobby Braddock, Kenny Chesney, Vince Gill, Emmylou Harris, Gayle Holcomb, Alan Jackson, Roger Miller, Billy Sherrill, Ricky Skaggs and Dwight Yoakam at the Ryman Auditorium on September 24.
